1. *Novine* su postale sastavni deo našeg života. (Newspapers have become an integral part of our life.)

2. Čitaoci *novina* uživaju u čitanju različitih vrsta članaka. (Newspaper readers enjoy reading various types of articles.)

3. *Novinari* su odgovorni za istraživanje i izveštavanje o događajima. (Journalists are responsible for researching and reporting on events.)

4. U prošlosti, *novine* su bile jedan od najvažnijih izvora informacija. (In the past, newspapers were one of the most important sources of information.)

5. *Novinama* se pristupa preko interneta u mnogim zemljama. (Newspapers are accessed via the internet in many countries.)